	autocmd Filetype python inoremap ;if if ±:<Enter><Tab><++> <Esc>k^f±li<Backspace>
	autocmd Filetype python inoremap ;var ±= <++> <Enter><++> <Esc>k/±<Enter>li<Backspace>
